WEBVTT

00:01:59.312 --> 00:02:05.248
Well, I think it's because
our policymakers don't believe

00:02:05.272 --> 00:02:10.097
that things like attraction
and the way relationships are built

00:02:10.121 --> 00:02:12.331
is changeable or educable.

00:02:13.262 --> 00:02:14.607
Why?

00:02:15.204 --> 00:02:19.198
Well, our policymakers currently
are Generation X.

00:02:19.658 --> 00:02:22.317
They're in their 30s to 50s.

00:02:22.931 --> 00:02:26.489
And when I'm talking to these guys
about these issues,

00:02:26.513 --> 00:02:28.502
